replies.txt_content:
更多附魔MOD的BUG
Change the enchantment ids in the moreenchants config to something different and try to reload it.Got there eventually by adding 100 to each ID, and it worked! Thanks for the help guys <3

似乎解决办法是打开MOD的配置文件 把相关的ID都加100试试
